&lt;p&gt;This side project is partnering with myÂ friend, &lt;a href=&quot;https://id.linkedin.com/in/suliskh&quot;&gt;Kukuh Sulistyo&lt;/a&gt;, he is a front-end engineer. He will help me to code this from ground-up. Weâ€™re really excited to work withÂ this.&lt;/p&gt;
